+# @ai-fable/tools
+
+Tool definitions for the AI Browser Agent.
+
+## Scripts
+
+```bash
+pnpm build      # Compile TypeScript
+pnpm dev        # Watch mode
+pnpm lint       # Run ESLint
+pnpm typecheck  # Type check without emitting
+pnpm clean      # Remove build artifacts
+```
